Instalação de aplicativos básicos:

sudo apt install gimp gnome-shell-pomodoro gufw pdfarranger printer-driver-escpr psensor ttf-mscorefonts-installer
snap install skype teams-for-linux


Instalação de aplicativos complementares:

sudo apt install gddccontrol gnome-boxes obs-studio soundconverter steam
snap install discord mc-installer


Habilitar Flatpak:

sudo apt install flatpak
flatpak remote-add --if-not-exists flathub https://flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo


Instalar Flatpaks:

flatpak install flathub com.usebottles.bottles
flatpak install flathub io.github.shiftey.Desktop
flatpak install flathub com.unity.UnityHub


Instalar externo:

Anaconda Navigator
